      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "You are truly the most Finnish Finn to have ever lived. Even in death
    you continue to be a national role model, becoming somewhat of a legend in our
    times. The story of your life reaches international news and inspires a global
    adaptation of Finnish culture. The line to your funeral is even longer than the
    one at Tokmanni when they gave out a free \xE4mp\xE4ri last weekend."
