      m_Calls: []
  m_text: Just like a true Finn, you lived quite an unremarkable life. You managed
    to gather some Sisu, but you mostly kept for yourself and did things your own
    way. Which in itself is very Finnish, so maybe you had it nailed down after all!
    That is at least what your family and friends seem to think as they mourn you,
    but sooner than later manage to move on.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
